266
00:19:15,760 --> 00:19:16,960
Teacher.

267
00:19:27,600 --> 00:19:31,080
Impossible.

268
00:19:32,600 --> 00:19:33,840
Impossible.

269
00:19:34,880 --> 00:19:36,160
Xiaofei, what's wrong?

270
00:19:36,160 --> 00:19:37,000
What's wrong?

271
