You too.

298
00:21:02,960 --> 00:21:04,080
We should go.

299
00:21:07,760 --> 00:21:08,520
Be good.

300
00:21:13,760 --> 00:21:14,520
Let's go.

301
00:21:38,720 --> 00:21:39,480
Let's go.

302
00:22:13,480 --> 00:22:15,480
How many days have you been playing?

303
00:22:16,600 --> 00:22:18,200
How did you become like this?

304
00:22:18,360 --> 00:22:20,560
You have stubble on your face, you know?

305
00:22:21,360 --> 00:22:22,200
Come.

306
00:22:22,200 --> 00:22:23,520
Stand up.

307
00:22:25,040 --> 00:22:26,280
Look at yourself.

308
00:22:26,280 --> 00:22:27,940
Do you look like a human being?

309
00:22:28,920 --> 00:22:29,480
I'm telling you,

310
00:22:29,480 --> 00:22:30,800
if you keep this up,

311
00:22:30,800 --> 00:22:33,040
you'll get worms all over.

312
00:22:33,040 --> 00:22:34,570
You will be totally ruined.

313
00:22:36,640 --> 00:22:38,170
I really don't understand.

314
00:22:39,360 --> 00:22:40,360
You have hands and feet,

315
00:22:40,360 --> 00:22:41,560
you are young.

316
00:22:41,840 --> 00:22:44,770
Are you just going to slack off and wait to die at home?

317
00:22:45,040 --> 00:22:45,960
Let me tell you,

318
00:22:46,600 --> 00:22:47,600
tomorrow,

319
00:22:47,920 --> 00:22:49,780
go out and find a job immediately.

320
00:22:49,800 --> 00:22:52,320
If I catch you being lazy at home again,

321
00:22:52,960 --> 00:22:54,480
you're going out to fish.

322
00:22:54,800 --> 00:22:57,040
Got it. I'll go look for a job tomorrow.

323
00:22:58,600 --> 00:22:59,280
Alright, alright.

324
00:22:59,280 --> 00:23:00,200
Take a shower.

325
00:23:00,600 --> 00:23:01,960
Wash your hair and get some rest.

326
00:23:01,960 --> 00:23:03,090
Don't play anymore.

327
00:23:03,600 --> 00:23:04,400
Go.

328
00:23:04,920 --> 00:23:06,360
I'm telling you, don't play anymore.

329
00:23:06,360 --> 00:23:08,620
I know. How many times have you said that?

330
00:23:08,960 --> 00:23:09,760
Hurry up.

331
00:23:25,360 --> 00:23:26,400
What should we do?

332
00:23:46,280 --> 00:23:47,240
It's okay.

333
00:23:47,560 --> 00:23:48,920
The boss won't forget about me.

334
00:23:48,920 --> 00:23:50,650
He must be busy with something.

335
00:24:09,640 --> 00:24:10,640
Stop the car!

336
00:24:10,640 --> 00:24:12,360
Stop!

337
00:24:12,880 --> 00:24:13,600
Stop!

338
00:24:22,760 --> 00:24:23,600
Boss!

339
00:24:24,520 --> 00:24:25,520
Why are you here?

340
00:24:25,840 --> 00:24:26,720
I...

341
00:24:27,240 --> 00:24:28,280
I called you,

342
00:24:28,280 --> 00:24:29,540
but you didn't answer.

343
00:24:29,600 --> 00:24:30,600
So I asked Zhu Xiaoyu.

344
00:24:30,600 --> 00:24:31,680
She said you were here today,

345
00:24:31,680 --> 00:24:32,880
so I came to find you.

346
00:24:34,200 --> 00:24:35,560
Do you need something from me?

347
00:24:35,560 --> 00:24:37,320
Nothing special.

348
00:24:37,320 --> 00:24:40,160
You mentioned before

349
00:24:40,160 --> 00:24:41,400
that after graduation,

350
00:24:41,400 --> 00:24:43,000
you'd help me find a job.

351
00:24:43,000 --> 00:24:44,880
I've been too bored staying at home lately,

352
00:24:44,880 --> 00:24:46,160
so I thought I'd ask you.

353
00:24:46,160 --> 00:24:47,200
Is that it?

354
00:24:48,600 --> 00:24:49,560
Just in time.

355
00:24:49,560 --> 00:24:51,840
The logistics company happens to be short of hands.

356
00:24:51,840 --> 00:24:53,000
And

357
00:24:53,000 --> 00:24:54,040
I'll put in a word for you,

358
00:24:54,040 --> 00:24:55,680
and you can report for work tomorrow.

359
00:24:55,680 --> 00:24:56,400
Really?

360
00:24:56,400 --> 00:24:56,840
Yes.

361
00:24:57,120 --> 00:24:58,400
That's great, boss.

362
00:24:58,400 --> 00:24:59,720
Don't worry, I'll definitely work hard.

363
00:24:59,720 --> 00:25:00,520
No problem.

364
00:25:00,520 --> 00:25:02,160
I believe in you. Keep it up.

365
00:25:02,640 --> 00:25:03,560
Let's go, sir.

366
00:25:03,560 --> 00:25:04,360
Let's go, sir.

367
00:25:05,880 --> 00:25:06,600
What are you doing?

368
00:25:06,600 --> 00:25:07,720
I'm going with you.

369
00:25:07,720 --> 00:25:08,520
Get back!

370
00:25:10,000 --> 00:25:10,760
Well,

371
00:25:10,760 --> 00:25:12,360
I still have a lot of

372
00:25:12,360 --> 00:25:13,960
important things to deal with later.

373
00:25:13,960 --> 00:25:15,480
So it's not very convenient.

374
00:25:15,480 --> 00:25:16,720
I know, you do your thing.

375
00:25:16,720 --> 00:25:17,800
Let's have a drink tonight when you're done.

376
00:25:17,800 --> 00:25:18,960
It's been a while.

377
00:25:21,520 --> 00:25:22,360
I'm very busy.

378
00:25:22,840 --> 00:25:23,840
I still have

379
00:25:23,840 --> 00:25:26,300
a lot of important things to deal with later.

380
00:25:26,600 --> 00:25:27,930
Let's do it another day.

381
00:25:30,840 --> 00:25:31,720
Got it.

382
00:25:32,120 --> 00:25:32,520
See you at the company then.

383
00:25:32,520 --> 00:25:33,400
Let's go, sir.

384
00:25:34,120 --> 00:25:35,000
Drive safely, sir.

385
00:25:35,000 --> 00:25:36,040
Let's go, sir.

386
00:25:42,000 --> 00:25:43,200
Take care, boss.

387
00:26:08,280 --> 00:26:10,080
You're drinking here? I'm back!

388
00:26:12,280 --> 00:26:13,440
Eating this?

389
00:26:16,320 --> 00:26:17,080
This

390
00:26:17,320 --> 00:26:20,360
is called peanuts and salted fish with liquor.

391
00:26:20,360 --> 00:26:21,560
A lifetime of happiness

392
00:26:21,560 --> 00:26:22,800
follows you.

393
00:26:22,800 --> 00:26:24,080
What do you know?

394
00:26:24,400 --> 00:26:25,880
Look what I bought for you.

395
00:26:27,480 --> 00:26:28,440
Pig's head meat.

396
00:26:30,200 --> 00:26:31,360
Cold dishes.

397
00:26:33,360 --> 00:26:35,290
You have to eat this when drinking.

398
00:26:36,520 --> 00:26:37,520
Did you find a job?

399
00:26:38,800 --> 00:26:40,200
It's a piece of cake.

400
00:26:40,200 --> 00:26:42,400
Could this little thing stump your son?

401
00:26:44,440 --> 00:26:45,960
You don't have a diploma,

402
00:26:46,400 --> 00:26:47,800
or any educational background.

403
00:26:47,800 --> 00:26:49,600
What kind of job could you find?

404
00:26:52,120 --> 00:26:52,980
Telecom fraud?

405
00:26:53,160 --> 00:26:54,090
Pyramid scheme?

406
00:26:54,200 --> 00:26:55,120
Let me tell you,

407
00:26:55,120 --> 00:26:56,040
those are illegal jobs.

408
00:26:56,040 --> 00:26:57,120
You can't do them.

409
00:26:57,320 --> 00:26:59,450
Why do you look down on your son so much?

410
00:26:59,680 --> 00:27:01,920
My boss, Lin Jiaming,

411
00:27:01,920 --> 00:27:04,200
arranged for me to work at his logistics company.

412
00:27:04,200 --> 00:27:06,240
Ordinary people can't even get in.

413
00:27:07,680 --> 00:27:09,120
That Lin Jiaming again.

414
00:27:09,840 --> 00:27:11,000
Didn't I tell you

415
00:27:11,000 --> 00:27:12,520
to stay away from him?

416
00:27:12,760 --> 00:27:13,680
Have you not learned

417
00:27:13,680 --> 00:27:14,480
your lesson

418
00:27:14,480 --> 00:27:15,800
from last time?

419
00:27:16,080 --> 00:27:17,840
Why do you always think of him like that?

420
00:27:17,840 --> 00:27:19,520
He promised to arrange a job for me last time

421
00:27:19,520 --> 00:27:20,560
and take care of my future.

422
00:27:20,560 --> 00:27:21,960
Now he has.

423
00:27:22,320 --> 00:27:23,780
You always worry too much.

424
00:27:25,200 --> 00:27:26,080
Anyway,

425
00:27:26,080 --> 00:27:26,960
let me tell you,

426
00:27:27,120 --> 00:27:28,000
this time,

427
00:27:28,000 --> 00:27:29,280
you need to be careful.

428
00:27:30,000 --> 00:27:32,600
You can never be too careful.

429
00:27:32,600 --> 00:27:33,600
Understand?

430
00:27:33,600 --> 00:27:35,040
I understand.

431
00:27:35,040 --> 00:27:36,160
I got it, Dad.

432
00:27:36,760 --> 00:27:37,840
Just don't worry.

433
00:27:38,400 --> 00:27:40,600
When your son makes money in the future,

434
00:27:40,800 --> 00:27:42,920
you can just stay on this boat

435
00:27:43,200 --> 00:27:45,060
and count on me to provide for you.

436
00:27:51,280 --> 00:27:52,160
Have a piece of meat.

437
00:27:52,160 --> 00:27:54,420
Eat up. This pork head meat is very fresh.

438
00:27:58,720 --> 00:27:59,520
Is it good?

439
00:28:17,600 --> 00:28:19,160
Such bland food.

440
00:28:20,040 --> 00:28:21,120
You've been eating it for so long.

441
00:28:21,120 --> 00:28:22,640
Can you still swallow it?

442
00:28:23,400 --> 00:28:24,480
If you eat it long enough,

443
00:28:24,480 --> 00:28:25,480
it's all the same.

444
00:28:31,400 --> 00:28:32,800
If you don't want to eat it,

445
00:28:32,800 --> 00:28:34,800
don't offend the people here.

446
00:28:35,440 --> 00:28:36,360
Get out early.

447
00:28:37,920 --> 00:28:39,120
You mean Lin Jiaming?

448
00:28:40,120 --> 00:28:41,180
It doesn't matter.

449
00:28:41,440 --> 00:28:42,720
Anyway,

450
00:28:43,360 --> 00:28:44,690
it's not the first time.

451
00:28:45,120 --> 00:28:47,000
Behind Lin Jiaming is

452
00:28:47,000 --> 00:28:48,000
the Lin Group.

453
00:28:49,640 --> 00:28:50,700
Aren't you afraid?

454
00:28:54,000 --> 00:28:55,040
But if I'm afraid,

455
00:28:55,840 --> 00:28:57,400
should I just be a coward?

456
00:28:58,360 --> 00:28:59,640
If you hide your head,

457
00:29:00,000 --> 00:29:01,600
they will cut off your hands.

458
00:29:01,760 --> 00:29:02,840
If you hide your hands,

459
00:29:02,840 --> 00:29:04,370
they will cut off your feet.

460
00:29:04,640 --> 00:29:05,570
Instead of that,

461
00:29:05,920 --> 00:29:07,880
it's better to go all out and fight.

462
00:29:08,360 --> 00:29:09,620
Who loses and who wins,

463
00:29:10,600 --> 00:29:11,660
is not certain yet.

464
00:29:12,840 --> 00:29:14,960
Those are your own hands and feet.

465
00:29:17,680 --> 00:29:19,210
What if it were your family?

466
00:29:19,960 --> 00:29:21,320
Then I can't back down even more.

467
00:29:21,320 --> 00:29:22,640
Because family

468
00:29:23,200 --> 00:29:24,730
is my absolute bottom line.

469
00:29:28,600 --> 00:29:29,960
You are still too young.

470
00:29:29,960 --> 00:29:32,020
You don't know how ruthless they are.

471
00:29:33,040 --> 00:29:34,920
I warned you.

472
00:29:35,560 --> 00:29:37,480
Take care of yourself.

473
00:29:40,840 --> 00:29:41,600
Thanks.

474
00:29:41,960 --> 00:29:43,280
Another day,

475
00:29:43,280 --> 00:29:44,320
I'll play chess with you.
